1. Objective

Testing the Tic-Tac-Toe application to ensure that user management, game mechanics, and UI features work as expected.

2. Scope
In Scope
Account creation
Login/Logout
Game board functionality
Turn management
Winner detection
Draw detection
Difficulty selection
Hint functionality
New Game / Reset
Profile
Game History
Language switching
Theme switching

3. Test Approach
Functional Testing
Validate all user flows and business logic

UI Testing
Verify layout, labels, buttons, themes, and responsiveness

Compatibility Testing
Test application behavior in supported browsers

Regression Testing
Verify existing functionality after fixes or updates

4. Test Environment
Windows 11
Chrome (latest)
Firefox (latest)
Edge (latest)

